{"tid":1996982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"徐英偉掌權後民政署：陶輝「牌照屋」將按程序8工作天內巡查後按證據辦事","createTime":"2020-05-01T10:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T10:32:14.000Z","uid":21470,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"65f332038f7a590e32e6dc41ec79b3447ad8918d","tid":1996982,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"助理警務處長陶輝：配合調查牌照屋是否違規<br />\n01.05.2020 18:02<br />\n<br />\n有報道指，助理警務處長陶輝將清水灣碧水新村，一間不可轉讓或出租的「牌照屋」作民宿出租，涉嫌違反條款，以及無牌經營旅館。陶輝下午在清水灣現身，指關注單位被指涉嫌違法，亦知道事件正由地政總署及民政總署調查，會遵守規則行事，亦會與相關部門合作，但無回應他有無出租「牌照屋」。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署回應傳媒提問時說，有關處所未領取旅館牌照，轄下的牌照事務處會跟進，如有足夠證據證明涉及無牌經營旅館，會採取檢控行動。牌照處在接獲舉報後，會在8個工作天內巡查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284580&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1284580%26csid%3D261_341&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=b9dc9ee9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1284580&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2e2e92f5eee394d6fa3f6543b5d71899ffaa3fe5","tid":1996982,"uid":134863,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"做大戲。官字兩個口"},{"pid":"f5b30c4c5d75043ae97fc826dc095dd93692f10c","tid":1996982,"uid":52423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"8日乜證據都冇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb331d6deaf0d12c5846cbfbc3b938d0bd0c1c2","tid":1996982,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"證據就一定夠，係想睇佢點幫自己人姐，斷估陶輝唔係推自己老婆出黎頂掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad1d4a6528727c8c58996925ca9c01bac3a49cc","tid":1996982,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5b30c4c5d75043ae97fc826dc095dd93692f10c","tid":1996982,"uid":52423,"like":3,"disli